body:
Support mobile onboarding bulk category creation.

**Endpoint:** `POST /api/v1/categories/bulk`

**Request Body:**
```json
{
  "categories": [
    { "name": "Food", "type": "EXPENSE", "color": "#FF5733" },
    { "name": "Salary", "type": "INCOME", "color": "#33FF57" }
  ]
}
```

**Response:** Array
